        </li>
        <li>
            <p>The third misunderstanding: financial management is concerned about all day financial products. Always pay attention to their financial products will increase the time of sunk costs. Good investment strategy is often staring at a promising product, and then long-term holding, do not frequent replacement. Case:You spent two hours watching the stock in the morning, you lost 2 hours to study and work time.</p>
