    <p>
        The most scientific family financial law: &quot;4321 distribution law&quot;
        The assets are divided into four parts, 40% for investment, 30% for consumption, 20% for savings, and 10% for insurance. With a constant hybrid strategy, after an asset rises, the total amount of the asset is reduced and it is evenly distributed among the other assets.
    </p>
    <p><strong>Case:</strong>If you have a monthly salary of 10,000, you can use 4,000 yuan to finance, 3,000 yuan to spend 2,000 yuan to save, 1,000 yuan to buy insurance, if your investment earned 2,000 yuan, or your salary rose 2,000 yuan, you can put This extra out of 2000 yuan and then in accordance with the &quot;4321&quot; ratio of the average distribution to the front of the four parts.</p>
